Class WorldStructurePieceQuarterSymmetrical.BlockWrapper

java.lang.Object
org.cyclops.evilcraft.world.gen.structure.WorldStructurePieceQuarterSymmetrical.BlockWrapper
Enclosing class:
WorldStructurePieceQuarterSymmetrical
public class WorldStructurePieceQuarterSymmetrical.BlockWrapper extends Object
This is a wrapper class, which wraps around a Block and pairs with it the metadata for that specific blockState instance.
